==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[professional]] [[writer]]; one whose occupation is to draw [[contract]]s or prepare [[writing]]s.
# {{obsolete}} One whose business is to place [[money]] at [[interest]]; a [[broker]].
# A writing master.

====Quotations====
''"Scrivener (enters with a paper in hand):
Here is the indictment of the good Lord Hastings,
Which in a set hand fairly in engrossed
That is may be today read o'ver in Paul's.
And mark how well the sequel hangs together:
Eleven hours I have spent to write it over..."''

-''Shakespeare's Richard III 3.6''

